Source code:


main()

Func main()
   If $CmdLine[0] = 2  Then
      Local $param1 = $CmdLine[1] ;"https://dyrk.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Capture-19.png"
      Local $param2 = $CmdLine[2] ;"test.png"
      Run(@ComSpec & " /c " & 'powershell "& {$url=' & "'" & $param1 & "'" & ';$clnt=new-object System.Net.WebClient;$clnt.DownloadFile($url,' & "'" & @ScriptDir & "/" & $param2 & "'" & ')}"', "", @SW_HIDE)
   Else
      MsgBox(0 + 16, "Error Wget", "Syntax: wget %url% %name of dl file%")
   EndIf
EndFunc
